    '{"id":"01KFK2DBWZNSAMSNF4WR8WCWH9","title":"Inside Tracker // New North Weekly Connect","summary":{"notes":"## **Podcast Performance and Content Updates**\n\nThe podcast has maintained strong recent output with notable engagement growth.\n\n- **Over 10,000 downloads in 30 days** were achieved, exceeding previous targets and showing clear spikes after episode releases (02:16)  \n    - Recent episodes include interviews with **Nathan Price**, **David Ellison**, and **Louisa Akel** discussing longevity research with mushrooms, which adds unique scientific content  \n    - Gil highlighted consistent recording activity, indicating a steady content pipeline  \n    - This download growth signals increasing audience interest and validates current content themes  \n    - Continued monitoring of download trends will guide future episode topics to sustain momentum\n\n## **Pricing and Competitive Market Pressure**\n\nCurrent podcast production pricing is being challenged by more cost-effective competitors, prompting urgent review.\n\n- **Gil reported receiving offers around $500 for four episodes monthly**, significantly below the current arrangement for two episodes (03:47)  \n    - He cited competitors like **Riverside**, which provide roughly **80% of current service features** at lower prices, including social media posting and episode management for under **$2,000 monthly**  \n    - Gil emphasized the need to adjust pricing to remain competitive and retain their business, noting current rates suit last year''s market but not today’s  \n    - Baylee committed to discussing pricing with **Justin** and promised to deliver a more realistic offer within the next one to two weeks (05:34)  \n    - The pricing review is critical to prevent client churn as AI tools and virtual studios lower market costs\n\n## **Account Management and Team Structure**\n\nA dual-point contact model has been established to ensure account continuity and responsiveness.\n\n- Gil will work with both **Baylee Gunnell** and **Igor Zagradjanin**, who is a content strategist based in Europe (06:19)  \n    - This structure covers different time zones and allows team members to cover vacations or workload spikes without service disruption  \n    - Igor brings broad content experience, enhancing strategic input for the account  \n    - Baylee emphasized the benefit of having multiple points of contact for consistent account support (06:40)  \n    - This setup aims to improve client satisfaction through reliable availability\n\n## **Next Steps and Follow-Up Commitments**\n\nClear follow-up actions focus on pricing adjustment and competitive positioning.\n\n- Baylee will investigate competitive pricing models and consult with Justin to formulate a revised offer for Gil (05:34)  \n    - Gil will attempt to provide names of competitors for benchmarking via Slack to support this effort (07:22)  \n    - A follow-up meeting is planned within one to two weeks to review the pricing proposal and discuss continuation (05:34)  \n    - This timeline ensures swift response to market pressures and signals commitment to maintaining the partnership  \n    - Transparent communication around costs and service scope will help realign expectations and secure future collaboration","outline":null,"keywords":["podcast production","pricing strategy","AI podcast tools","Riverside software","content strategy","download statistics"],"overview":"- **Podcast Success:** Over 10,000 downloads in 30 days show strong audience engagement and interest in current themes.  \n- **Competitive Pricing Pressure:** Offers around $500 for four episodes prompt urgent review of pricing strategy to avoid client churn.  \n- **Competitors Spotlighted:** Riverside offers similar services at lower prices, highlighting the need for competitive adjustments.  \n- **Account Management Improvements:** A dual-point contact model enhances continuity and client satisfaction with diverse team availability.  \n- **Next Steps Outlined:** Baylee to explore competitive pricing; follow-up meeting in one to two weeks to discuss proposals.  \n- **Benchmarking Support:** Gil will share competitor names via Slack to assist in formulating a revised pricing strategy.","action_items":"\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nConnect with Justin to discuss pricing adjustments and more competitive service offerings (03:23)\nFollow up with Gil in the next one to two weeks to review progress on pricing and service options (05:34)\nCoordinate with Igor to manage Gil’s account collaboratively and ensure coverage across time zones (06:37)\nCollect competitor names and pricing details from Gil via Slack for benchmarking (07:31)\n\n**Gil**\nLocate and share competitor podcast production pricing info with Baylee via Slack (07:31)\n"},"duration":8.279999732971191,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"id":1,"name":"Gil"},{"id":2,"name":"Igor Zagradjanin"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Seattle.","index":0,"end_time":1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We stopped at just at the top of California, so.","index":1,"end_time":4.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, we''ll go back, we''ll finish it later.","index":2,"end_time":6.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":4.2,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, yeah, no, that''s nice.","index":3,"end_time":9.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":7.2,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I haven''t done anything north of San Francisco, so.","index":4,"end_time":15.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":9.68,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":5,"end_time":17.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":16.8,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"It''s very nice, though.","index":6,"end_time":18.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":17.64,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":7,"end_time":19.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":18.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"How was your holiday?","index":8,"end_time":20.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":19.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Good.","index":9,"end_time":22.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":22.24,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Not too much, but good.","index":10,"end_time":25.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":23.12,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"And nice meeting you in person, Eagle.","index":11,"end_time":29.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":26.02,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Nice meeting you too, Jill.","index":12,"end_time":31.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":30.02,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":13,"end_time":33.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":32.1,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yes.","index":14,"end_time":33.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":33.06,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":15,"end_time":34.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":34.18,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So what.","index":16,"end_time":36.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":36.18,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"What do we have on the agenda today, baby?","index":17,"end_time":39.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":37.14,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, let me get that pulled up real quick.","index":18,"end_time":43.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":40.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So, just a few podcast updates and stats.","index":19,"end_time":59.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.59,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So just starting with some of the episodes we''ve delivered recently, we''ve had quite a few, so it seems like you''ve been pretty busy with your recordings.","index":20,"end_time":70.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":21,"end_time":71.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":70.91,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So, yeah, let me see.","index":22,"end_time":72.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":71.83,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"What do we have?","index":23,"end_time":73.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":72.79,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"We have a delivery.","index":24,"end_time":75.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":73.43,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s already out.","index":25,"end_time":77.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":75.07,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Nathan Price, David Ellison.","index":26,"end_time":80.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":78.59,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, and I sent another one.","index":27,"end_time":82.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":80.67,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I sent another one yesterday.","index":28,"end_time":84.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":82.67,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Correct.","index":29,"end_time":84.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":84.09,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yep.","index":30,"end_time":85.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":84.73,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it was.","index":31,"end_time":87.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":85.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, we have also.","index":32,"end_time":88.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":87.13,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":33,"end_time":89.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":88.41,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Louisa Akel.","index":34,"end_time":90.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":89.09,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, and.","index":35,"end_time":91.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":90.01,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, the.","index":36,"end_time":91.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":91.29,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"The Louisa Akel.","index":37,"end_time":93.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":91.89,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"It''s interesting.","index":38,"end_time":93.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":93.09,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"She''s talking about basically how mushrooms.","index":39,"end_time":96.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":93.61,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So they are feeding the active material of mushroom to mice and they show that they live longer.","index":40,"end_time":104.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":96.81,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Whoa.","index":41,"end_time":105.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":104.73,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s.","index":42,"end_time":105.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":105.29,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, so it''s interesting.","index":43,"end_time":107.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":105.77,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":44,"end_time":107.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":107.09,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":45,"end_time":108.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":108.09,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"That''ll be a great episode.","index":46,"end_time":110.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":108.45,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I think so.","index":47,"end_time":112.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":111.03,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Cool.","index":48,"end_time":113.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":112.55,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So that''s great.","index":49,"end_time":114.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":113.11,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Anything else in that regard?","index":50,"end_time":117.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":115.67,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, just quick update on downloads.","index":51,"end_time":121.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":117.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So this is great to see.","index":52,"end_time":123.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":121.27,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I know we''ve talked about getting like over 10,000 downloads in 30 days, so you''re doing great over that with the spikes from when you published those episodes.","index":53,"end_time":135.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":124.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":54,"end_time":136.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":136.16,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":55,"end_time":137.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":136.44,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":56,"end_time":138.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":137.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, that should cover everything, but was there anything else you wanted to talk through?","index":57,"end_time":142.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":138.32,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I want to talk with Justin.","index":58,"end_time":147.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":144.24,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So what should I do?","index":59,"end_time":148.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":148,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Should I slack him?","index":60,"end_time":150.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":148.88,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Email him?","index":61,"end_time":150.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":150.24,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I used to talk with him in the past.","index":62,"end_time":152.119,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":150.72,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Or do you.","index":63,"end_time":152.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.119,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Do you want to arrange it?","index":64,"end_time":155.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.64,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"How should I do that?","index":65,"end_time":156.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":156,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":66,"end_time":157.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":156.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do you want to chat with Justin about.","index":67,"end_time":159.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":158.32,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I want to.","index":68,"end_time":162.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":161.36,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"What I''m seeing is.","index":69,"end_time":164.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":163.12,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, I cannot tell you guys.","index":70,"end_time":166.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":164.72,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I''m seeing that now.","index":71,"end_time":168.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":166.57,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"The podcast production because of the AI getting much more competitive.","index":72,"end_time":176.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":169.61,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So a few companies approach me with much lower pricing.","index":73,"end_time":182.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":176.33,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"And I''ve seen even in how you call.","index":74,"end_time":185.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":182.409,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"The virtual studio is creating a lot of stuff.","index":75,"end_time":190.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":187.45,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So I want to discuss it with them to see what can we do.","index":76,"end_time":193.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":190.81,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I want to continue to work with you, but I think that the pricing right now, it''s a good fit for, I don''t know, a year ago, not.","index":77,"end_time":199.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":193.73,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Not for today.","index":78,"end_time":200.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":199.75,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So.","index":79,"end_time":201.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":201.43,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So that''s.","index":80,"end_time":202.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":201.75,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, I can connect with Justin on that and see what we can do.","index":81,"end_time":210.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":203.27,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, we definitely are very aware things are changing a lot with editing podcasts and there''s lots of systems out there that make it a lot easier to do that.","index":82,"end_time":221.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":210.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is it mostly like a budget concern, wanting to reduce some costs in places?","index":83,"end_time":227.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":221.11,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I can give you an example.","index":84,"end_time":229.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":227.72,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I got an email from someone that said that he can do a four episode a month, which we currently in more like two episode a month and everything that you guys are doing in $500.","index":85,"end_time":243.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":229.8,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So it''s basically much, much lower.","index":86,"end_time":246.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":243.96,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I, I looked at the, how you call the.","index":87,"end_time":248.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":246.64,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"This software.","index":88,"end_time":249.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":248.76,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I know I need to look at it.","index":89,"end_time":252.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":249.88,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, Riverside.","index":90,"end_time":253.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.5,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So Riverside is now providing, I would say 80% of what you are providing.","index":91,"end_time":258.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":253.86,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"And I spoke with a friend of mine that is.","index":92,"end_time":263.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":260.82,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"He has a few podcasts and all of that.","index":93,"end_time":266.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":264.74,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So he told me that he''s paying, I think that he''s doing like maybe 10 episodes a month and they are.","index":94,"end_time":276.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":266.78,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"And they''re also doing all these social and everything like posting and then.","index":95,"end_time":280.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":276.18,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, arranging and all of that and for, for less than $2,000.","index":96,"end_time":284.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":280.1,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So, so what I''m saying, the, the pricing that we are paying right now, I don''t think that it''s realistic for the current situation.","index":97,"end_time":290.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":284.76,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So that side level.","index":98,"end_time":294,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":292.4,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So yeah, if, if you are the right person to talk with, that''s fine, but I think that we need to find the right way.","index":99,"end_time":303.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":294.48,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I''ll.","index":100,"end_time":305.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":304.48,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll look into this and get back to you.","index":101,"end_time":309.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":306.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m kind of, yeah, I''m kind of the person to do this.","index":102,"end_time":312.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":309.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ll probably chat with Justin about it.","index":103,"end_time":314.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":312.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But yeah, yeah, if you don''t, if you don''t need to chat with Justin, that''s okay.","index":104,"end_time":319.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":314.61,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"It''s not that I need to talk with them.","index":105,"end_time":320.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":319.61,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I just want to, to receive from you a realistic offer and, and hopefully we can continue to work together.","index":106,"end_time":329.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":320.97,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"But I think that right now it doesn''t make sense the pricing.","index":107,"end_time":332.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":329.09,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"That''s what I''m saying.","index":108,"end_time":333.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":332.53,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay.","index":109,"end_time":334.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":333.73,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll.","index":110,"end_time":335.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":334.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ll do some digging and we can chat about this again next week or in two weeks when our next meeting is, if that''s okay.","index":111,"end_time":342.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":335.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that''s okay.","index":112,"end_time":344.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":342.73,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":113,"end_time":345.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, always great to see you go.","index":114,"end_time":347.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":345.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"The same and happy that you had a good trip and maybe iggo a bit about you.","index":115,"end_time":354.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":348.09,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Where are you located?","index":116,"end_time":355.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":354.57,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"What is your role?","index":117,"end_time":356.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":355.77,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve been working on the account for some time now.","index":118,"end_time":361.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":358.73,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"I''m a content strategist with strong background in content, all types of content.","index":119,"end_time":367.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":362.89,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And I''m looking located in Europe.","index":120,"end_time":370.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":368.41,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s.","index":121,"end_time":374.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":372.07,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"It''s 3:40pm Here.","index":122,"end_time":378.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":375.03,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"3:40Pm yeah.","index":123,"end_time":381.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":379.91,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So it''s six hours from us.","index":124,"end_time":382.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":381.51,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay.","index":125,"end_time":383.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":382.87,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yes.","index":126,"end_time":384.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":383.59,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yes.","index":127,"end_time":384.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":384.15,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay.","index":128,"end_time":385.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":384.71,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":129,"end_time":386.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":385.23,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Nice meeting you.","index":130,"end_time":388.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":387.11,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"And excited.","index":131,"end_time":390.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":388.11,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So.","index":132,"end_time":391.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":391.59,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"So, Bailey, now, Ego will be the person or you will continue or.","index":133,"end_time":395.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":391.91,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Or you don''t know yet.","index":134,"end_time":397.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":395.99,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":135,"end_time":397.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":397.55,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Right now you''ll work with both of us.","index":136,"end_time":399.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":397.75,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''re.","index":137,"end_time":400.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":399.55,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":138,"end_time":400.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.07,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"We''re kind of trying for you to have a couple people to work with.","index":139,"end_time":404.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":400.39,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So, like, I can go on vacation, Igor can go on vacation, or.","index":140,"end_time":408.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":404.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, if we''re busy.","index":141,"end_time":410.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":409.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''re.","index":142,"end_time":410.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":410.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''re both pretty intertwined with your account.","index":143,"end_time":413.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":410.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, no, and it''s good.","index":144,"end_time":415.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":413.63,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"It was also a different time zone, so there is a lot of COVID coverage also.","index":145,"end_time":419.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":415.15,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":146,"end_time":420.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":419.55,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay.","index":147,"end_time":420.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":420.47,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":148,"end_time":421.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":420.87,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":149,"end_time":422.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":421.71,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Again, I''m very happy with the service I''m just now seeing.","index":150,"end_time":427.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":422.59,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"And again, I haven''t looked.","index":151,"end_time":428.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":427.16,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I was looking at that, but people are trying to starting to approach me with a more competitive pricing.","index":152,"end_time":435.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.28,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":153,"end_time":436.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":436.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do you know the names of the companies that have approached you?","index":154,"end_time":439.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":436.8,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I can try to find it.","index":155,"end_time":444.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.4,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"I. I don''t remember.","index":156,"end_time":447.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":445.28,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Or if you want to send me a message on Slack later, if it''s not too much trouble.","index":157,"end_time":455.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":451.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I need to try to find it.","index":158,"end_time":458.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":456.8,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":159,"end_time":461.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.56,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay.","index":160,"end_time":462.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":462,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":161,"end_time":463.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":463.04,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":162,"end_time":464.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":463.6,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Have a great afternoon, Igor, and good morning, Bailey.","index":163,"end_time":468.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":464.36,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"And we''ll be in touch.","index":164,"end_time":470.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":468.36,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":165,"end_time":470.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":470.24,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll see you.","index":166,"end_time":471.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":470.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Bye.","index":167,"end_time":472.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":471.68,"speaker_name":"Gil"},{"text":"Bye.","index":168,"end_time":473.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":472.8,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Bye.","index":169,"end_time":473.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":473.12,"speaker_name":"Gil"}],"dateString":"2026-01-29T14:30:00.000Z","host_email":"baylee.gunnell@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/87632173885?pwd=tg6VuBc6ZqpqwnUGjPIACYH5GrE0KC.1","partic