,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":736.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So it.","index":311,"end_time":744.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":743.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"If what you did is perfect.","index":312,"end_time":746.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":744.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I tested the forms and it''s all good.","index":313,"end_time":747.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.06,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I just.","index":314,"end_time":748.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.14,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I couldn''t get into 2fa.","index":315,"end_time":750.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":748.94,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I could.","index":316,"end_time":751.299,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":750.58,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I Seems like that''s been an issue.","index":317,"end_time":752.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":751.299,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I like, ah, I want to go do this myself but I couldn''t do it.","index":318,"end_time":758.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.18,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So.","index":319,"end_time":758.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":758.42,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":320,"end_time":758.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":758.58,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"One thing there, is it updated?","index":321,"end_time":760.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":758.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is it necessary to set up a redirect from the previous upcoming URL to the on demand or is that automatically happening in the system?","index":322,"end_time":768.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":761.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Automatically happened, yeah.","index":323,"end_time":770.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":769.61,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":324,"end_time":771.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":770.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it tested last night a