le.","index":338,"end_time":816.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":815.15,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m like, I know.","index":339,"end_time":817.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":816.31,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":340,"end_time":817.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":817.39,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, trust me, we''re doing that.","index":341,"end_time":818.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":817.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, it didn''t work.","index":342,"end_time":821.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":819.07,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then this is done.","index":343,"end_time":829.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":825.23,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"I just wanted to ask you.","index":344,"end_time":830.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":829.71,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"Oh, I.","index":345,"end_time":832.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":831.31,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"You mentioned that there were 13 leads under hack, but I only saw eight.","index":346,"end_time":838.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":832.19,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"I don''t know, which stuff were you looking at or.","index":347,"end_time":843.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":838.68,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"Yeah, I was looking in forms, and when I took another look at it.","index":348,"end_time":847.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":843.32,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Let me just show you here.","index":349,"end_time":849.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":847.6,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Just do a quick share again.","index":350,"end_time":854.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":852.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I think this one rep, Dennis Berger.","index":351,"end_time":861.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":857.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":352,"end_time":862.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":862.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"K