:377,"end_time":1413.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1410.89,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And we have this version which is a screenshot somehow photoshopped into another screenshot or something.","index":378,"end_time":1421.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1414.81,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Right?","index":379,"end_time":1422.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1421.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":380,"end_time":1422.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1422.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it''s almost to show, like, what the.","index":381,"end_time":1424.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1422.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like a highlight of the person''s profile if you click on it.","index":382,"end_time":1428.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1425.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think we need to give you a new screen.","index":383,"end_time":1437.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1435.54,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"You just need screenshots or you need video sequences.","index":384,"end_time":1439.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1437.02,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We can work with screenshots.","index":385,"end_time":1441.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1440.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because this looks also strange if you really look at it.","index":386,"end_time":1449.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1445.46,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Is that the search?","index":387,"end_time":1451.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1450.9,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It''s probably.","index":388,"end_time":1452.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1452.02,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Oh, I think there''s some temporary version of the search.","index":389,"end_time":1454.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1452.62,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Some older one.","index":390,"end_time":1455.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1454.66,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":391,"end_time":1456.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1455.7,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":392,"end_time":1460.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1460.18,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Then I create new screenshots, send them over.","index":393,"end_time":1463.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1460.78,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":394,"end_time":1464.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1463.69,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":395,"end_time":1464.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1464.33,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":396,"end_time":1475.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1475.05,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"This is a little bit.","index":397,"end_time":1476.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1475.45,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Not sure what else came from.","index":398,"end_time":1478.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1476.57,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"What is the idea here?","index":399,"end_time":1483.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1482.57,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I''m not.","index":400,"end_time":1484.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1483.85,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It''s really hard to say how that looks or what you''re doing with those.","index":401,"end_time":1486.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1484.33,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Things because.","index":402,"end_time":1487.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1486.81,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We have all these different, like, pictures.","index":403,"end_time":1493.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1489.46,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We have a laptop and then we have this, which is completely different background.","index":404,"end_time":1498.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1493.98,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"How is that any.","index":405,"end_time":1498.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1498.26,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"How is that going to look afterwards?","index":406,"end_time":1500.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1498.94,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Well, it''s showing, like, transitions.","index":407,"end_time":1502.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1500.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, like, use, like on the computer, and then it goes into the actual, like, platform.","index":408,"end_time":1508.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1502.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":409,"end_time":1512.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1512.1,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It''s really important also just to read, like, with the text on the left side so that it''s.","index":410,"end_time":1518.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1513.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It kind of pulls it together.","index":411,"end_time":1519.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1518.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s.","index":412,"end_time":1520.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1519.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s hard to show through a storyboard exactly how the video is going to come together.","index":413,"end_time":1524.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1520.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":414,"end_time":1525.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1525.06,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Maxing also look at that maybe and.","index":415,"end_time":1529.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1527.38,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"See if we find better screenshots for the whole story here.","index":416,"end_time":1532.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1529.38,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":417,"end_time":1533.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1532.66,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"But I mean, is that.","index":418,"end_time":1536.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1534.98,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"So those screenshots, I guess they are already in the SharePoint somewhere, so we can see what you have, right?","index":419,"end_time":1543.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1537.54,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"Yeah, they were.","index":420,"end_time":1544.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1544.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They were from videos.","index":421,"end_time":1545.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1544.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s probably also why the resolution is not the greatest.","index":422,"end_time":1549.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1547.15,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It''s maybe easier if you don''t need the video, like, to animate it.","index":423,"end_time":1552.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1549.67,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So I don''t know what you need.","index":424,"end_time":1554.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1553.87,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"If you need the animated video.","index":425,"end_time":1556.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1554.91,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"No, we can do the screenshots and then we can just like, mimic what a mouse would do on the screen and how it would pop up.","index":426,"end_time":1562.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1557.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that would be easier to create just screenshots.","index":427,"end_time":1566.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1563.63,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I Would think awesome.","index":428,"end_time":1572.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1568.03,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":429,"end_time":1574.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1573.8,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right, what else do you have?","index":430,"end_time":1579.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1577.48,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So I was thinking through a few weeks ago we talked about like a benchmark analysis report that may be enticing to prospects.","index":431,"end_time":1587.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1580.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I was, I was thinking through what we could do for that.","index":432,"end_time":1589.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1587.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so I was thinking like a utilization and skills benchmark for IT consulting firms.","index":433,"end_time":1595,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1590.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So they would answer about five high level questions and get a short report that compares their utilization, their bench health and their staffing efficiency to similar firms in the industry.","index":434,"end_time":1605.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1595.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''m not sure if you guys have your own proprietary data that we would be able to say this is a benchmark for the industry or if we should just use external research.","index":435,"end_time":1615.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1607.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But it would intentionally be modeled to show or use industry data and PSA patterns so that we can basically show like how a company can grow or scale or reduce their bench, all of these factors by using a tool like Desi Dollo.","index":436,"end_time":1632.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1617.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what they would submit is like their firm size, just a range, the estimated utilization, an estimate of their bench size, how long it takes roughly to staff a project, and how skills are currently tracked today.","index":437,"end_time":1646.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1634.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like a checklist of we use Excel or we use whatever the next tool.","index":438,"end_time":1651.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1646.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then they would fill that out and then an automated report would be generated with Desi dollar branding and their measures compared to industry standards.","index":439,"end_time":1661.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1653.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean we could pull data from Desi Dialo, but it''s not probably an industry standard.","index":440,"end_time":1672.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.72,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I guess we can get the numbers from somewhere, but I''m not sure.","index":441,"end_time":1675,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1672.28,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"The question is whom are we targeting with that?","index":442,"end_time":1677.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1675.61,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Who would fill that out?","index":443,"end_time":1678.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1677.57,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"That is a bit.","index":444,"end_time":1679.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1678.65,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I''m not so sure.","index":445,"end_time":1682.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1681.05,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I would tell my.","index":446,"end_time":1684.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1682.73,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Initially when I was building it, I had resource managers in mind.","index":447,"end_time":1686.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1684.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, they.","index":448,"end_time":1690.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1689.37,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Question is, do they have all the utilization data for the whole company?","index":449,"end_time":1699.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1695.85,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Depends on the size of the company and if they.","index":450,"end_time":1703.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1699.93,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, one.","index":451,"end_time":1706.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1705.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One logic tree that we typically build into these offers for someone that doesn''t know what like the data that we''re asking for is an option to say I don''t know and then that pushes them into a demo call.","index":452,"end_time":1717.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1706.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that may work.","index":453,"end_time":1721.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1720.11,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, So you have a draft of that somewhere.","index":454,"end_time":1735.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1727.31,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, we can share that with you.","index":455,"end_time":1737.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1736.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Share that with us and see what we can provide.","index":456,"end_time":1740.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1738.13,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve been building a lot of these in Claude code and using like Lovable as a front end.","index":457,"end_time":1745.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1741.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''ve been seeing a lot of success with these.","index":458,"end_time":1748.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1746.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What is the idea?","index":459,"end_time":1749.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1748.61,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We put that where on the.","index":460,"end_time":1750.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1749.49,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Like on LinkedIn or then so yeah.","index":461,"end_time":1754.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1750.85,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So we would set up an ad that would point to it, but we would need it to go to a landing page we would probably just set up a subdomain so that they could be like offers dot or something like that on the Desi Dollo primary domain.","index":462,"end_time":1768.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1754.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s where they would land and fill out the form and then it would auto generate a PDF and I would.","index":463,"end_time":1773.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1768.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They would need to give us their email address or what is the.","index":464,"end_time":1776.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1773.9,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, we would collect their email address and things like that.","index":465,"end_time":1778.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1776.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":466,"end_time":1779.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1778.94,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":467,"end_time":1782.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1782.27,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And just share that we take a look.","index":468,"end_time":1784.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1782.55,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, all right, that sounds good.","index":469,"end_time":1786.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1784.63,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And then Max, I know you had some questions around the N8N flow.","index":470,"end_time":1789.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1786.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Was there anything specifically you wanted to dive into?","index":471,"end_time":1791.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1789.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, a lot, but I don''t think four minutes will be sufficient.","index":472,"end_time":1798.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1793.55,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"So maybe we should just shift that next week, but maybe not Friday.","index":473,"end_time":1802.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1798.27,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"But do you have access yet?","index":474,"end_time":1804.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1802.11,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Max, we can''t share our N8N.","index":475,"end_time":1807.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1804.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They can''t because of configuration.","index":476,"end_time":1809.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1807.48,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"Okay.","index":477,"end_time":1810.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1809.72,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"This is one for all of your customers or.","index":478,"end_time":1813.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1811.08,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we have one account for.","index":479,"end_time":1814.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1813.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we just have it split up by folders.","index":480,"end_time":1816.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1814.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":481,"end_time":1818.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1817.4,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Because we have it all on a.","index":482,"end_time":1819.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1818.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We have our own private server set up.","index":483,"end_time":1822,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1820.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, I see.","index":484,"end_time":1825.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1822,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, we have access to the.","index":485,"end_time":1827.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1825.88,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"To the clay.","index":486,"end_time":1828.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1827.64,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We can share and export out of clay but that''s a similar.","index":487,"end_time":1832.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1829.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s all of our clients browser broken out by folders in one account.","index":488,"end_time":1835.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1832.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":489,"end_time":1838.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1837.6,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":490,"end_time":1842.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1842.24,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So if you guys can land on which text you want on the images for the ads, we''ll send over a test email so you can see how those are performing and then let us know about the screenshots on the video and then we''re.","index":491,"end_time":1856.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1842.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re rocking and rolling.","index":492,"end_time":1857.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1856.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think we''re going to be able.","index":493,"end_time":1858.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1857.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To Launch and the LinkedIn outreach from Bettina''s account.","index":494,"end_time":1861.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1858.48,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"When are you going to start?","index":495,"end_time":1862.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1861.2,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"That would start at the same time as the emails.","index":496,"end_time":1864.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1862.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Today is beginning of next week.","index":497,"end_time":1866.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1864.99,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"That''s the idea.","index":498,"end_time":1867.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1866.51,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yep.","index":499,"end_time":1868.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1867.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s all running under Betina basically.","index":500,"end_time":1870.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1868.11,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, we have to inform her so she''s.","index":501,"end_time":1875.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1872.59,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"She knows what''s coming.","index":502,"end_time":1877.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1875.71,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right Max, anything from your side?","index":503,"end_time":1880.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1878.429,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, no, I will just have a different meeting with Colin.","index":504,"end_time":1884.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1881.39,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"Okay.","index":505,"end_time":1885.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1885.15,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":506,"end_time":1886.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1885.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What do you think when you can update the.","index":507,"end_time":1888.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1886.07,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"The website?","index":508,"end_time":1889.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1888.61,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Because I want to get the website.","index":509,"end_time":1890.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1889.09,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Also done like the images and things like that.","index":510,"end_time":1895.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1892.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":511,"end_time":1897.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1895.97,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Natalie, can we have that maybe done on Monday?","index":512,"end_time":1900.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1898.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, definitely.","index":513,"end_time":1902.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1901.09,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, we can have the images updated in every two on Monday.","index":514,"end_time":1906.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1903.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":515,"end_time":1908.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1907.57,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":516,"end_time":1911.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1910.29,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Anything else?","index":517,"end_time":1912.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1911.57,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Nope, that''s it from our side.","index":518,"end_time":1913.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1912.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you very much for your time and I hope you have an awesome weekend.","index":519,"end_time":1916.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1913.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know you guys are ending your day.","index":520,"end_time":1917.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1916.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It groupings five.","index":521,"end_time":1919.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1918.17,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"}],"dateString":"2026-01-30T14:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86344108572?pwd=qdakcUFJbrjywReJlBZ3DxNLrBYqXb.1","participants":["tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,joachim.giesen@uni-jena.de,guille.santana@marketersindemand.com,nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com,voelker@data-assessment.com,bebinger@decidalo.com,osbaldeston@data-assessment.com,pollex@data-assessment.com,rabeler@data-assessment.com","tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com","joachim.giesen@uni-jena.de","guille.santana@marketersindemand.com","nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com","voelker@data-assessment.com","bebinger@decidalo.com","osbaldeston@data-assessment.com","pollex@data-assessment.com","rabeler@data-assessment.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KFNT5BJ8PJ4QXJADX5E0YQ4W","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
