  '[{"text":"Add notes to Ron’s task to prioritize design work for end of day and confirm scheduling with Gary for next day’s development (05:36)","completed":false},{"text":"Review script document and identify sections to cut to streamline ''on the job training'' video and related videos (24:02)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Paula on outreach list segmentation and refresh campaign using HubSpot lists or prior contacts with revised messaging (15:18)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide feedback and make recommendations to video production team on potential frame cuts and timing adjustments (19:18)","completed":false},{"text":"Keep Josh updated on video review status and progress for visibility (38:47)","completed":false},{"text":"Manage scheduling and communication with outreach contacts Nikita, Nazaire, and Nasser to resolve scheduling link issues and confirm meetings (13:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Open tasks for Gary promptly upon receiving design completion to keep development on track (06:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Share metaboards and video materials with Josh for review of product demo videos (33:25)","completed":false},{"text":"Continue monitoring podcast episode 15 and outreach stats for progress and prepare for upcoming episode recording (10:11)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor client expectations on timing and communicate feasibility of same day edits and turnaround (06:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Reach out to Nasser to resolve scheduling issues and coordinate outreach meetings (13:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Review scripts for ''on the job training'' and other videos to provide cut recommendations to reduce exposition and improve timing (26:26)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate live or asynchronously with Baylee and Paula to optimize video timing and pacing before finalizing (20:12)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide feedback on video audio and music quality; prefer consistent pacing as in ''action plans''