ps for PTO Exchange (56:17)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist in sharing campaign and audit presentations and related documentation (08:38)","completed":false},{"text":"Help lead the database assessment and manage developer resources to explore automation or improved workflows for cleanup (42:32)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide full presentation and report links to Carmen and wider team including the HubSpot audit and campaign tracking overviews (05:24)","completed":false},{"text":"Prioritize removing duplicate testimonial and replacing/removing AI-generated or stock images on homepage (24:58)","completed":false},{"text":"Support setup of standardized data definitions, property mapping, and cleanup workflows within HubSpot in collaboration with New North team (35:54)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare a summary of next steps and processes as part of existing retainer, clarifying scope and timeline (38:09)","completed":false},{"text":"Flag and encourage quick removal of duplicate testimonials and images lacking authenticity on website (20:41)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide user perspective and feedback on CTA, navigation, and marketing content authenticity (14:28)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist in evaluating quality of contact database and prioritizing clean filters (44:32)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
