  '[{"text":"Continue refining paid media ROI reporting by compiling MQL, SQL, and client numbers with historical spend data for 2023-2025 (05:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide more detailed data inputs to integrate reallocation of paid media budget by month between platforms (07:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Investigate why certain MQLs revert to earlier lifecycle stages and communicate insights for data accuracy (25:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Pull receipts and actual paid media spending for each month in 2025 and note month(s) of budget reallocations (08:10)","completed":false},{"text":"Deliver updated Microsoft Copilot Consulting page today (21:35)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare website performance analysis reports comparing one year post-launch metrics versus pre-launch (22:45)","completed":false},{"text":"Create reports showing MQLs from marketing sources with reasons for non-conversion to identify marketing vs. sales issues (23:50)","completed":false},{"text":"Troubleshoot HubSpot reporting to improve accuracy of MQL, SQL, opportunity, and customer attribution by lifecycle dates (06:40)","completed":false},{"text":"Explore and define tools like sales decks or one-pagers to aid sales teams in advancing SQLs and opportunities (15:30)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist in analyzing lead detail and closed reason data to identify common sales pipeline challenges contributing to low customer conversions (16:15)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor Jeff’s feedback on AI landing page updates and communicate expected delivery timeline (20:20)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
