,"start_time":1379.63,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Her, I said mid right now is kind of plopping images to show variation versus placement.","index":371,"end_time":1394.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1388.08,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And also like when we go through.","index":372,"end_time":1396,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1394.04,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The content review process, like we''re going to be providing images, we''re going to like, we''re not there yet.","index":373,"end_time":1401.479,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1396,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But I think that because we opened.","index":374,"end_time":1403.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1401.64,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"It up to executives for feedback, that''s what just we''re getting, right?","index":375,"end_time":1405.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1403.12,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":376,"end_time":1405.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1405.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":377,"end_time":1406.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1405.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then for the disclosures, like, we don''t, I don''t want to have to scroll, scroll, scroll.","index":378,"end_time":1411.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1406.84,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think it''s like, how do we go across?","index":379,"end_time":1414.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1411.48,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":380,"end_time":1415.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1414.73,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The bottom super small text, like, like shorter.","index":381,"end_time":1419.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1415.37,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think that that would, you know, that would help.","index":382,"end_time":1423.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1420.41,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Scroll down a little bit more.","index":383,"end_time":1427.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1425.69,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We''ll have to.","index":384,"end_time":1434.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1433.69,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Personal, personal.","index":385,"end_time":1437.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1435.93,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I don''t think that people know what Ponce Bank Direct is.","index":386,"end_time":1443.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1438.09,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So what I would say is personal business banking.","index":387,"end_time":1448.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1444.5,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I, I, I think we have to.","index":388,"end_time":1454.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1452.5,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Figure out a way where we go and separate like mortgages and I don''t know, I have to think about that a little bit more.","index":389,"end_time":1464.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1454.94,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think some companies do like personal banking is like deposits and then they.","index":390,"end_time":1473.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1464.3,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Have let, you know, mortgages and you know, home, something like that.","index":391,"end_time":1478.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1473.61,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then they have like small business banking or business banking.","index":392,"end_time":1485.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1480.41,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But then they also like, if they have a lot of commercial, they, they lead with the commercial.","index":393,"end_time":1489.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1485.81,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I just don''t want any one area.","index":394,"end_time":1491.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1489.93,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"To feel like their division is a sub click.","index":395,"end_time":1494.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1491.61,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":396,"end_time":1494.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1494.49,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because everybody''s secondary.","index":397,"end_time":1496.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1494.81,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"You know, they think that theirs is the most important.","index":398,"end_time":1498.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1496.41,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I want to think about Ponce Bank.","index":399,"end_time":1502.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1500.79,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Direct a little bit.","index":400,"end_time":1503.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1502.83,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think that we need to have a different call out for.","index":401,"end_time":1507.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1503.87,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Online Only services.","index":402,"end_time":1511.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1509.67,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And I wonder if it almost makes sense to, to have like maybe like a pop up on the homepage to say, you know, almost like guide them.","index":403,"end_time":1523.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1512.07,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"In the direction they want to go.","index":404,"end_time":1525.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1523.99,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like if.","index":405,"end_time":1525.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1525.43,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because if somebody lands on this page.","index":406,"end_time":1529.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1526.35,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"That is not looking for any local services.","index":407,"end_time":1532.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1529.91,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":408,"end_time":1533.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1533.15,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But they want the national thing, they''re.","index":409,"end_time":1536.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1533.51,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Not going to know where to click.","index":410,"end_time":1537.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1536.59,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So I wonder if it makes sense.","index":411,"end_time":1539.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1537.71,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"To say like we don''t have Ponse Bank Direct on the menus.","index":412,"end_time":1545.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1539.15,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We have the microsite page that we use for that use case when we advertise and the searchability.","index":413,"end_time":1551.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1545.71,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But do we give them a prompt that.","index":414,"end_time":1555.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1552.73,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, we still need some way to naturally guide them towards that page if they land organically.","index":415,"end_time":1558.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1555.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So a few that I''m thinking about, I think the pop up could work.","index":416,"end_time":1561.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1558.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think also I want to create a variation where we have rotating banner in that hero that is kind of going through all these offers and the business banking, personal direct, everything, mortgages.","index":417,"end_time":1570.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1561.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, a few different ideas that we can come up with there.","index":418,"end_time":1573.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1570.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Victor, I saw you raise your hand as well.","index":419,"end_time":1574.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1573.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":420,"end_time":1574.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1574.57,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"But even just thinking about the service that points the bank direct offers, Christina, they''re not your typical like SoFi kind of bank where you''re able to do, you know, business.","index":421,"end_time":1584.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1574.89,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"Business and personal banking.","index":422,"end_time":1585.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1584.6,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"They only offer CDs, SBA lending, like they only offer a specific number of things.","index":423,"end_time":1592.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1585.96,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"So to call out like we''re missing that.","index":424,"end_time":1594.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1592.2,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"I think it just needs to be specific to the type of audience that.","index":425,"end_time":1598.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1595.48,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"That offers.","index":426,"end_time":1599.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1598.92,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"Yeah, no, I, I know but the.","index":427,"end_time":1601.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1600.2,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Think about the, the page right now is, is set up that, that way too.","index":428,"end_time":1605.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1601.92,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I mean you could on that page.","index":429,"end_time":1607.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1605.56,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Still provide them, you, you know, infographics, like there''s still like educational material you can provide.","index":430,"end_time":1615.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1607.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And honestly like we''re, we''re looking to assess the products and see if there''s you know, the ability to add to that, you know, so, so more to come there.","index":431,"end_time":1624.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1615.9,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"One thing that I do want to.","index":432,"end_time":1627.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1625.22,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Create is a campaigns and like a.","index":433,"end_time":1631.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1627.1,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Promotions page almost where any promotion will live there.","index":434,"end_time":1635.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1631.02,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So for example, like when we start to need to advertise.","index":435,"end_time":1640.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1635.34,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Special features, we''ll.","index":436,"end_time":1644.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1642.69,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We''ll put all the terms and conditions and all that jazz there and use that as the driver for some of our calls to action versus having it land on a homepage that we''re going to get pushed back because the disclosure is at the bottom.","index":437,"end_time":1660.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1644.81,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":438,"end_time":1660.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1660.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The way I did it at MCU.","index":439,"end_time":1661.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1660.49,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Was we would have a special promotion page and like every section would have like the hero and the disclosures.","index":440,"end_time":1668.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1661.81,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So it''s always one click away, depending on what we were offering.","index":441,"end_time":1672.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1668.92,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, so that''s.","index":442,"end_time":1675.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1674.16,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think that''s pretty much it at.","index":443,"end_time":1678.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1675.2,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"At this time.","index":444,"end_time":1679.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1678.32,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Do we have a.","index":445,"end_time":1680.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1679.6,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"A rates?","index":446,"end_time":1681.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1680.56,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Did we ever think of.","index":447,"end_time":1682.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1681.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Did we ever discuss rates?","index":448,"end_time":1684.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1682.16,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I don''t think we did, but it would probably be under, like, resources.","index":449,"end_time":1693.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1687.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think rates may need to kind of be front and center.","index":450,"end_time":1700.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1693.59,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"That''s a lot of people, like, search that you could.","index":451,"end_time":1703.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1700.87,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Maybe you could do, like, rate rates.","index":452,"end_time":1705.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1703.55,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And current promotions or something like that.","index":453,"end_time":1707.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1705.07,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Rates for us needs to be built.","index":454,"end_time":1712.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1709.11,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Out as a dynamic table.","index":455,"end_time":1713.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1712.27,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So if we have a content hero that has a 4% rate, it needs to be not tied to that specific hero, but tied to a chart.","index":456,"end_time":1725.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1714.07,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And it''s got to be built in a way that dynamically adjusts those.","index":457,"end_time":1729.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1725.65,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So we''re only adjusting rates in one spot and not having to search the site for wherever we put a promotion.","index":458,"end_time":1739.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1731.09,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So that''s something that we need to.","index":459,"end_time":1741.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1739.57,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"To talk about.","index":460,"end_time":1742.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1741.29,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":461,"end_time":1744.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1744.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I remember looking at this when you and I first had some conversations.","index":462,"end_time":1748.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1744.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So.","index":463,"end_time":1750.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1749.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, what I can see here is that they built it in a similar structure where it''s easy to.","index":464,"end_time":1754.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1750.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To see all of this data flow through.","index":465,"end_time":1755.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1754.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":466,"end_time":1756.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1756.14,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And, like, you see how the disclosure is a really nice, like, per product.","index":467,"end_time":1760.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1756.94,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like, I think that that''s going to really help us when we get to.","index":468,"end_time":1763.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1760.54,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":469,"end_time":1763.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1763.42,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And you see, like, they have it.","index":470,"end_time":1766.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1764.86,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"There, like personal and, like, they have digital banking.","index":471,"end_time":1768.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1766.1,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like, maybe we call it digital banking, but the brand is Ponzi Bank Direct.","index":472,"end_time":1771.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1768.98,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like.","index":473,"end_time":1772.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1771.9,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":474,"end_time":1772.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1772.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think that that would be, you know, cool.","index":475,"end_time":1775.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1772.42,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Go.","index":476,"end_time":1775.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1775.14,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Go back up.","index":477,"end_time":1775.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1775.42,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because I think there was one other thing that sparked my.","index":478,"end_time":1778.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1775.86,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I mean, sorry, go back to.","index":479,"end_time":1780.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1779.26,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, the routing number needs to be there.","index":480,"end_time":1786.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1783.31,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then you see how they have that, like, top menu where it has branches.","index":481,"end_time":1790.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1786.11,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like, I think that is a good way to separate some of the menus where you''re still giving them visibility, but not necessarily clouding, you know, crowding.","index":482,"end_time":1800.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1790.67,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":483,"end_time":1800.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1800.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Having a super nav allows us to have all of those extra buttons without people, like, all right, well, where.","index":484,"end_time":1805.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1800.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Where do I go?","index":485,"end_time":1806.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1805.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I do, like, the.","index":486,"end_time":1808.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1807.3,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The thing that I built out, like, if you go to personal, like, hover over that menu, you see how, like, the current personal or something on the right pops up.","index":487,"end_time":1816.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1809.54,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I do like that, because that is where we could have, like, a feature promotion that''s getting that audience.","index":488,"end_time":1823.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1817.14,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":489,"end_time":1826.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1825.7,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So I think digital banking could be the digital services, but then also Ponzi.","index":490,"end_time":1832.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1826.18,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Bank Direct could be under there.","index":491,"end_time":1835.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1832.9,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":492,"end_time":1836.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1835.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"As.","index":493,"end_time":1837.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1837.42,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"As a.","index":494,"end_time":1838.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1837.78,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"As a way.","index":495,"end_time":1839.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1838.34,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So I think just a couple of Tweaks.","index":496,"end_time":1844.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1840.78,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Is it doable for you guys to.","index":497,"end_time":1848.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1846.38,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Provide sort of a, a slightly revamped policy bank homepage with then something that I can show investor relations, the, the direction and, and the foundation and it.","index":498,"end_time":1864.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1848.54,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Doesn''T have to be super built out but I just want them to see.","index":499,"end_time":1867.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1864.55,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Visually how even if it''s just the hero and you put placeholders for ads.","index":500,"end_time":1873.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1867.63,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":501,"end_time":1874.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1874.19,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So you could do the, the main nav and all the menus, the hero placeholders and then a footer.","index":502,"end_time":1881.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1874.55,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think that that would really help.","index":503,"end_time":1882.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1881.23,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Even if, if we do that for.","index":504,"end_time":1886.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1882.83,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like the, the careers too.","index":505,"end_time":1887.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1886.35,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"That might be nice to, to see.","index":506,"end_time":1890.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1887.63,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":507,"end_time":1891.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1890.67,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"All the other things we can layer in, you know, over time.","index":508,"end_time":1896.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1891.79,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":509,"end_time":1897.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1897.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I suspect a little bit more.","index":510,"end_time":1903.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1899.47,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Feedback to come through as we, as we go.","index":511,"end_time":1906.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1903.31,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But I think it''s really coming together.","index":512,"end_time":1909.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1906.99,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think it''s just now like with the feedback where you understand that we don''t need to like always use the brand elements together.","index":513,"end_time":1916.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1909.95,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like they''re fluid to be.","index":514,"end_time":1918.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1916.75,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"You know, for us white space is.","index":515,"end_time":1921.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1918.4,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Good and, and why.","index":516,"end_time":1923.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1921.84,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"What, what I mean, white space is.","index":517,"end_time":1925,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1923.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"It''s just more of a focus on the content than the imagery.","index":518,"end_time":1928.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1925,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So white space could be white background or it could be like a light, light color variation.","index":519,"end_time":1934.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1929.2,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Last thing I''ll mention is we just.","index":520,"end_time":1937.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1935.52,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Have to make sure that we are lockstep aligned on the blues.","index":521,"end_time":1940.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1937.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So anywhere we have the dark blue, it should be the ponsse pre existing blue, the teal and then the, that yellowy color.","index":522,"end_time":1952.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1941.12,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And the reason why, and I think it even makes more sense now that.","index":523,"end_time":1956.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1953.14,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We''Re making the change, is one of our biggest competitors.","index":524,"end_time":1959.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1956.62,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Jane.","index":525,"end_time":1959.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1959.38,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We were looking at some local competitors.","index":526,"end_time":1962.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1960.1,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"They use the, the blue and the, and the teal.","index":527,"end_time":1965.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1962.98,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And so if it''s too close we.","index":528,"end_time":1968.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1966.5,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Might get you know, a little bit of either pushback from them or just like hey, where''s your, you know, where''s your variation?","index":529,"end_time":1975.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1968.46,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":530,"end_time":1976.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1975.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Um, it''s perhaps our closest competitor for bank.","index":531,"end_time":1983.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1976.55,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then you know we can start.","index":532,"end_time":1988.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1985.99,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"To think about like, like you said like the rotating images, how many will need.","index":533,"end_time":1993.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1988.51,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So like for me it''s always going to be maybe something community, something product, something you know, careers related.","index":534,"end_time":2001.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1993.07,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And I don''t want to have too many.","index":535,"end_time":2003.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2001.75,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, I think like 4 is typically a good number that doesn''t get over cumbersome but still gives us to play with.","index":536,"end_time":2008.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2003.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":537,"end_time":2009.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2008.93,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then like where are you showing.","index":538,"end_time":2013.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2009.89,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like the possibilities for personalization, customization?","index":539,"end_time":2017.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2013.49,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So for example like with HubSpot we may be able to say good morning name.","index":540,"end_time":2024.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2018.05,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like that might be something cool that.","index":541,"end_time":2026.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2024.93,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"You put on the homepage to show how we''re connecting the big investment that we''re making with, you know, with that system.","index":542,"end_time":2034.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2026.49,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We do want to think about for the location pages and any of the.","index":543,"end_time":2043.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2037.24,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Imagery selections being super local.","index":544,"end_time":2045.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2043.2,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So Jane might be able to provide some just feedback when we get to the image selection for there.","index":545,"end_time":2052.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2046.76,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But I will caveat that right now.","index":546,"end_time":2055.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2052.84,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We have location pages that are built out by a third party vendor.","index":547,"end_time":2059.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2055.28,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We are now going to lose those.","index":548,"end_time":2063.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2061.03,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Pages when we convert or sunset that contract.","index":549,"end_time":2068.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2063.83,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So the local pages need to be.","index":550,"end_time":2070.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2068.63,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Built in a, in a way where.","index":551,"end_time":2072.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2070.55,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"They''Re almost feeding the hours and locations.","index":552,"end_time":2075.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2072.31,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"From whatever, you know, source.","index":553,"end_time":2078.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2075.51,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":554,"end_time":2079.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2078.91,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"If it fit, if it''s.","index":555,"end_time":2080.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2079.23,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Or maybe the opposite way.","index":556,"end_time":2081.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2080.63,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like, like Google needs to pick it up from our website.","index":557,"end_time":2084.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2081.99,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like does, does Ponzi have to follow.","index":558,"end_time":2087.639,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2084.63,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The process of updating our Google Pages for then the website to be updated?","index":559,"end_time":2090.879,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2087.639,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So like question though.","index":560,"end_time":2092.559,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2090.879,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"When we initially spoke with HUDs HubSpot one of the things that really attracted us is that they have that listing structure.","index":561,"end_time":2102.638,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2092.559,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So wouldn''t that be an integration from Hubs?","index":562,"end_time":2105.359,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2102.959,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Wouldn''t HubSpot be the main place where we are inputting and then it marries to the site?","index":563,"end_time":2110.799,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2105.359,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"That''s what we have to talk about, right?","index":564,"end_time":2112.719,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2111.119,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like how we, you know, how we set that up.","index":565,"end_time":2114.879,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2112.719,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because right now, don''t forget like we, we are managing in a lot of different places and also like the World Wide Web has hundreds and hundreds of, you know, sites that could list their hours and locations.","index":566,"end_time":2131.429,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2116.11,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Even ones that we don''t even know exist, they just pick it up.","index":567,"end_time":2135.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2131.429,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Some of it is user generated content where the user just goes in and you know, a random Joe Schmo will update our hours and we don''t even know about it.","index":568,"end_time":2142.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2135.23,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like unfortunately that''s just like the dynamic of that.","index":569,"end_time":2145.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2142.91,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We also want to pull in our ratings and reviews on the those and I''m trying to get a partnership going with Glassdoor so like we may be able to put it pull in ratings and reviews from Glassdoor.","index":570,"end_time":2158.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2147.95,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"You know, this all doesn''t have to be like phase one but like just to start to think about like if.","index":571,"end_time":2163.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2159.23,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"There''S anything that I''m saying that would trigger you to have to set the page up differently.","index":572,"end_time":2167.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2163.47,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like maybe we could start to think about it.","index":573,"end_time":2168.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2167.15,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, no, I just want to check into the integration capabilities that we have here with the tools before I say anything and personalization, things like that, definitely easy to bake in and we have fallback content.","index":574,"end_time":2179.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2168.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, I mean obviously we want, we just update in HubSpot and then all locations and everything are updated across the board.","index":575,"end_time":2186.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2180.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I just want to figure out the cleanest way to do stuff like that.","index":576,"end_time":2189.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2186.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":577,"end_time":2190.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2189.45,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But I think like, what Gene is.","index":578,"end_time":2191.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2190.21,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Focusing on is like even beyond kind of like our site, like, you know, what are the capabilities?","index":579,"end_time":2198.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2191.57,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because then we would have to update like our process.","index":580,"end_time":2202.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2199.21,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":581,"end_time":2202.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2202.49,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because right now we update in.","index":582,"end_time":2205.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2202.81,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"In uberall and it kind of whatever location pages that they built to be connected to it on the third party, like World Wide Web, like they update.","index":583,"end_time":2212.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2205.09,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right, right.","index":584,"end_time":2213.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2212.37,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":585,"end_time":2213.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2213.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It doesn''t.","index":586,"end_time":2214.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2213.85,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"It''s not going to work in the same way.","index":587,"end_time":2216.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2214.81,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But the local location pages are where we could have like local events.","index":588,"end_time":2223.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2217.69,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The little bit about the.","index":589,"end_time":2224.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2223.17,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"That team, specifically, that management team, what they offer specifically, if anything.","index":590,"end_time":2228.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2224.41,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then we also need to make sure that we have a process for our forms and like the, the building out of that and, and how we''re gonna make sure they''re secure and the captcha and all that.","index":591,"end_time":2243.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2230.26,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So yeah, like we''re getting way technical, into down the weeds.","index":592,"end_time":2247.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2244.82,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And you know, I know that that''s going to come when we start to build out each of the pages, but.","index":593,"end_time":2251.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2248.02,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s all good.","index":594,"end_time":2253.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2251.54,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"I love these conversations.","index":595,"end_time":2254.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2253.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Victor, I saw you raise your hand as well.","index":596,"end_time":2255.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2254.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":597,"end_time":2256.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2256.37,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"One of the things that I spoke with the customer rep on and HubSpot was buyer''s intent.","index":598,"end_time":2261.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2257.01,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"And I thought that that was a really interesting feature and that''s something that, you know, maybe Q2 of our website build.","index":599,"end_time":2267.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2261.73,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"But Christina and Jane, just to give you insight, buyer''s intent, the idea behind that is to see what companies are actually visiting our website.","index":600,"end_time":2277.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2267.81,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"And we''re actually able to collect the data from that.","index":601,"end_time":2280.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2277.41,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"So we''re able to see like if bank of America or other big companies or even smaller companies visit our website, we''re able to track those cookies and give that to our sales team as kind of leverage to maybe possibly make a connection with those.","index":602,"end_time":2294.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2280.45,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"With those things.","index":603,"end_time":2295.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2294.26,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"So just a code that would be embedded into the website in order for us to collect that data.","index":604,"end_time":2299.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2295.02,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"So just something that I wanted to throw out there as a potential visit for phase two, if possible.","index":605,"end_time":2304.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2299.3,"speaker_name":"victor garcia"},{"text":"Yeah, no, that''s good.","index":606,"end_time":2306.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2304.66,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then I know we''re over, but I did see a couple of like scrolled over, like new things.","index":607,"end_time":2312.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2306.9,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Is there anything you feel like, cool to share?","index":608,"end_time":2317.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2314.25,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because now I''m intrigued.","index":609,"end_time":2319.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2317.85,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":610,"end_time":2319.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2319.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Kia, did you want to dive in?","index":611,"end_time":2321.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2319.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":612,"end_time":2323.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2322.73,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"For, for the website?","index":613,"end_time":2324.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2323.13,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":614,"end_time":2325.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2324.81,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"No, the other stuff that we got.","index":615,"end_time":2327.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2325.69,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, I know we''ve been communicating a lot of our email as well.","index":616,"end_time":2330.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2328.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we had like the postcards and the.","index":617,"end_time":2332.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2330.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":618,"end_time":2333.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2333.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So here''s some other pages that we''ve been in the midst of designing as well.","index":619,"end_time":2336.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2333.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But we will take your new comments into.","index":620,"end_time":2345.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2343.86,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, no, like, these are all, all like awesome.","index":621,"end_time":2350.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2347.06,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But like, you know, you''ll see at the top.","index":622,"end_time":2352.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2350.3,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":623,"end_time":2352.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2352.58,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like if you go all the way, all the way to the top.","index":624,"end_time":2354.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2352.9,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like, I think a cleaner look would.","index":625,"end_time":2361.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2358.82,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Just be the, like the mobile app, maybe like a very like light shadow gradient or whatever.","index":626,"end_time":2368.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2361.82,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because.","index":627,"end_time":2368.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2368.04,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, product is not.","index":628,"end_time":2372.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2368.32,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"It''s like market diagnostic, I guess, basically.","index":629,"end_time":2376.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2373.8,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":630,"end_time":2376.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2376.2,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And so like you want people to focus in on that.","index":631,"end_time":2379.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2377.32,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Also we have to do a better.","index":632,"end_time":2381.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2379.96,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Job of getting you screenshots of our actual digital experience so you can overlay when.","index":633,"end_time":2385.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2381.04,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Anytime the mobile is.","index":634,"end_time":2386.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2385.48,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, that would be great.","index":635,"end_time":2389,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2388.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, no, I, I think this looks, this looks great.","index":636,"end_time":2394.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2390.36,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"My only other thing would be like, do like, where, where do we balance, like how much copy we have in.","index":637,"end_time":2404.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2397.96,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The heroes.","index":638,"end_time":2408.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2407.64,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But yeah, I, I think this looks really, really nice.","index":639,"end_time":2412.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2408.52,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Too bad we don''t have like online account opening, but we could actually say open now.","index":640,"end_time":2416.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2412.12,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Right.","index":641,"end_time":2417.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2416.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know.","index":642,"end_time":2418.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2418.2,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, no, this is.","index":643,"end_time":2422.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2421.07,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, well, we''ll take your feedback and syndicate it across all the pages we''ve designed.","index":644,"end_time":2430.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2426.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":645,"end_time":2431.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2431.23,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"All right, so I guess sync internally and just if you want to send me either Colin or Yugi, just like a summary of like what I''m going.","index":646,"end_time":2440.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2431.87,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"To expect to see by Friday, if I, if I can see anything or if not, just give me a date, I''ll go back and I''ll tell the team.","index":647,"end_time":2446.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2440.23,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And then what I''m probably going to do is for the next round of iterations, I''m going to convince Betty to like, get me actual like in person.","index":648,"end_time":2454.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2447.09,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Time with them to walk them through.","index":649,"end_time":2455.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2454.13,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Because I think what''s happening is again, they''re just, they''re just losing the context.","index":650,"end_time":2458.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2456.05,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"They''re looking at what they see and they''re not seeing the forward.","index":651,"end_time":2461.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2458.69,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"And I need everybody to be on.","index":652,"end_time":2464.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2462.21,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Board with it because if they''re not.","index":653,"end_time":2467.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2464.49,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Then, you know, we''re not going to be successful.","index":654,"end_time":2469.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2467.53,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"But I think overall, like really excited.","index":655,"end_time":2471.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2469.85,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"To kind of see how this is coming through.","index":656,"end_time":2473.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2471.98,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So.","index":657,"end_time":2473.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2473.46,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":658,"end_time":2474.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2473.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And on the website, we''re loading in the test contact, so we''ll be able to send over some updates on that tomorrow.","index":659,"end_time":2478.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2474.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I''ve been beating Google''s door down trying to get any email response from their user support team instead of these automated things.","index":660,"end_time":2485.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2479.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I''ll update you when I have any response from them.","index":661,"end_time":2488.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2485.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But Google is just.","index":662,"end_time":2489.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2488.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''re being Google, unfortunately.","index":663,"end_time":2492.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2490.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, no, I mean, that''s going to be a challenge because we need to start getting like.","index":664,"end_time":2495.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2492.3,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Like, I. I have a campaign for spring for Ponzi being direct, and we don''t have an ads account now.","index":665,"end_time":2501.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2495.62,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we''ve been.","index":666,"end_time":2502.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2501.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ve been emailing them, like, every three days, pretty much as soon as we can.","index":667,"end_time":2505.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2502.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":668,"end_time":2506.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2506.14,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Oh, wait.","index":669,"end_time":2509.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2508.54,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"The last.","index":670,"end_time":2509.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2509.18,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"What did I just want to say the last thing?","index":671,"end_time":2511.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2509.94,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Oh, the start to.","index":672,"end_time":2515.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2513.9,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"To give me, like, a forward head, think about what.","index":673,"end_time":2520.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2515.9,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"What teams I need to get involved.","index":674,"end_time":2521.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2520.02,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"With, because I want to start to think about the emails because once we get data in, like, I want to start to think about constant contact.","index":675,"end_time":2526.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2521.3,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Sunset, and let me know if we need to do any reconnecting for any of the social channels.","index":676,"end_time":2531.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2526.6,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"I think some of them got wonky with that issue that we had this week, and I think other than that, we''re.","index":677,"end_time":2535.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2531.12,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"We''re good.","index":678,"end_time":2536.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2535.48,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"So maybe at this time we could just cancel that other meeting that we had, because I think I covered pretty much everything that I wanted to share, so.","index":679,"end_time":2545.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2536.12,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":680,"end_time":2545.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2545.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":681,"end_time":2546.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2546.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we can cancel tomorrow''s meeting.","index":682,"end_time":2547.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2546.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, sounds good, guys.","index":683,"end_time":2549.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2548.04,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":684,"end_time":2549.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2549.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, thank you so much.","index":685,"end_time":2550.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2549.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you for the extra minutes as well.","index":686,"end_time":2551.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2550.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, bye.","index":687,"end_time":2552.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2552.26,"speaker_name":"christinazanca"}],"dateString":"2026-01-26T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85439302813?pwd=qMBHtkNo4lURIrnTCVFhLG0k15ZQca.1","participants":["tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com,jane.trachet@poncebank.net,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,victor.garcia@poncebank.net,rebecca.cruz@poncebank.net,guille.santana@marketersindemand.com,christina.zanca@poncebank.net","tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com","jane.trachet@poncebank.net","victor.garcia@poncebank.net","rebecca.cruz@poncebank.net","guille.santana@marketersindemand.com","christina.zanca@poncebank.net"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KFBXWYGDQHESGFDC5KB6S3SR","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.91,"bullets":["Confirmed HubSpot integration is functioning; contact records are loading as expected.","Christina outlined clear feedback on design balance and imagery direction for brochure and website.","Team will prepare updated homepage variants to show direction for investor and foundation audiences.","Identified need for dynamically updated rates table and clear separation for digital banking services.","Agreed to sunset third-party local pages; future location data will flow through internal systems."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Overall, like, this, this looks fantastic... well done for a first draft.","speaker":"christinazanca"},{"quote":"Buyer''s intent... just something that I wanted to throw out there as a potential.","speaker":"victor garcia"},{"quote":"We''re loading in the test contact, so we''ll be able to send over some updates on that tomorrow.","speaker":"colin costigan"}],"topics":["delivery","design","feedback","website","integration"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-vision","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-26T18:39:11Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Website Design and User Experience**\n\nThe website redesign focuses on balancing modern simplicity with brand cohesion to meet diverse executive and audience needs.\n\n- **Christina Zanca highlighted feedback from leadership emphasizing a cleaner balance between line drawings and stock images on brochures and the website, advising against layering both together excessively to avoid visual clutter** (06:56)  \n    - Betty preferred distinct use of either line drawings or stock photos, not both simultaneously.  \n    - The goal is to simplify the brand’s visual language for easier user focus and executive buy-in.  \n    - Future designs will incorporate more white space to reduce busy navigation and emphasize content.  \n    - This approach supports a more modern, sophisticated feel aligned with Ponce’s evolving brand identity.\n\n- **Feedback emphasized tailoring homepage content to four key audience segments: consumer (business and retail), community/foundation, investor relations, and staffing/recruiting** (09:01)  \n    - Executives want clearer representation of commercial and recruitment areas alongside community focus.  \n    - Homepage iterations will include specific content variations for general Ponce Bank, microsites, and recruitment to satisfy executive expectations.  \n    - The homepage will feature placeholders for core sections like hero banners and ads to visually represent these segments early.  \n    - This segmentation will help drive executive alignment and improve targeted messaging.\n\n- **Image selections must reflect current or futuristic themes and better local market relevance, avoiding outdated visuals that suggest stagnation** (11:10)  \n    - Executives noted overrepresentation of Hispanic imagery; diversity should include Caucasian, Bangladeshi, Indian, Asian, and Greek communities.  \n    - Historic images will be reserved for appropriate pages like \"About Us\" to maintain authenticity without undermining innovation.  \n    - Outdated ATM images risk negative perception; Ponce can provide updated photos to improve brand impression.  \n    - Incorporating these changes will better resonate with diverse local audiences and support brand inclusivity.\n\n- **Visual design adjustments include reducing repetitive blue bar elements and using them strategically to complement hero sections, with more white or light color space in subsections** (13:50)  \n    - Line drawings may be blended transparently or replaced with icons or solid color backgrounds in subsections to avoid overload.  \n    - Color palette alignment is critical: dark blue must match Ponsse’s existing brand blue, with teal and yellow accents carefully balanced to avoid confusion with competitor Jane.  \n    - These refinements aim to create a cleaner, more focused visual hierarchy supporting brand differentiation.  \n    - A limit of around four rotating hero banners is planned to keep user experience smooth without overwhelming content.\n\n## **Content Strategy and Navigation Structure**\n\nThe content organization and navigation will be redesigned to clarify product offerings and streamline user journeys for different banking services.\n\n- **Christina proposed separating personal banking, mortgages, and business banking into distinct navigation sections to avoid any division feeling secondary** (24:30)  \n    - Personal banking will include deposits and mortgages with clear calls to action.  \n    - Business banking will be highlighted equally to reflect its importance to executives and clients.  \n    - Ponce Bank Direct, offering limited products like CDs and SBA loans, will have a distinct callout or microsite to avoid confusion with full-service banking.  \n    - This approach ensures all client segments feel prioritized and find relevant information easily.\n\n- **A dedicated promotions and campaigns page will centralize all special offers and terms, reducing clutter and disclosure issues on the homepage** (27:10)  \n    - This page will serve as a landing spot for calls to action related to marketing campaigns.  \n    - The structure will replicate best practices from previous successful implementations at MCU for clarity and compliance.  \n    - Separating promotions supports easier updates and better user focus on core banking products.  \n    - This plan anticipates smoother marketing execution and regulatory alignment.\n\n- **Dynamic rate tables will be built so that updates propagate automatically site-wide, avoiding manual changes across multiple pages** (28:50)  \n    - This will allow a 4% or other rate updates to be managed in one place.  \n    - The system design follows existing structures for product-specific disclosures and digital banking sections.  \n    - Dynamic content management improves accuracy and reduces manual errors.  \n    - It enhances customer trust by ensuring current rates display consistently.\n\n- **Navigation menus will include a “super nav” to house extra buttons without crowding the interface, improving user clarity** (29:55)  \n    - Hover menus will showcase featured promotions or key products tailored to each audience segment.  \n    - Ponce Bank Direct will likely be nested under digital services to maintain brand clarity.  \n    - This layered navigation supports intuitive discovery across diverse banking products.  \n    - It aligns with user expectations for quick access to relevant info.\n\n## **Technical Integration and Data Management**\n\nThe website will integrate with HubSpot and other tools to streamline data handling, personalization, and location management.\n\n- **HubSpot is confirmed as the primary system for contact record management and location data, simplifying updates across platforms** (07:05)  \n    - HubSpot integration will allow centralized input of branch hours and locations feeding into the website.  \n    - This replaces fragmented management currently spread across multiple third-party platforms.  \n    - Leveraging HubSpot’s listing structure could improve accuracy and reduce manual workload.  \n    - Integration supports future scalability and data consistency.\n\n- **Localization efforts require building local pages that dynamically reflect accurate hours, events, and team information** (35:55)  \n    - Local content will be sourced from HubSpot or similar centralized tools to ensure consistency.  \n    - These pages will feature secure, well-designed forms with CAPTCHA to maintain data integrity.  \n    - The approach addresses the challenge of user-generated incorrect information on external sites.  \n    - It supports better customer engagement with community-specific content.\n\n- **Future phases may include embedding buyer’s intent tracking to identify companies visiting the website for sales leverage** (37:30)  \n    - This HubSpot feature tracks web visitors like Bank of America to support targeted outreach.  \n    - It requires embedding specialized code into the website.  \n    - Victor Garcia suggested this as a Q2 implementation to enhance sales intelligence.  \n    - This capability could improve lead generation and conversion rates.\n\n- **Personalization options like greeting users by name on the homepage are planned to enhance user experience** (33:28)  \n    - This builds on the investment in HubSpot’s CRM capabilities.  \n    - Location-specific images and content will improve relevance and engagement.  \n    - These features will be balanced with fallback content to maintain broad usability.  \n    - Personalization aims to deepen customer connection and loyalty.\n\n## **Project Management and Next Steps**\n\nThe team is aligned on next deliverables, timelines, and stakeholder engagement to secure executive buy-in and ensure smooth rollout.\n\n- **Christina requested a revamped homepage mockup focusing on main navigation, hero, placeholders, and footer to present to investor relations and foundation teams** (30:37)  \n    - This version will be a visual draft, not fully built, to facilitate early feedback.  \n    - A similar approach is planned for the careers section to show consistency.  \n    - The goal is to gain executive buy-in before proceeding with broader builds.  \n    - Colin and Yugi will coordinate delivery by Friday and communicate timelines.\n\n- **Additional rounds of homepage and microsite refinements are expected based on ongoing executive feedback** (17:05)  \n    - Christina plans to secure in-person walkthrough sessions with Betty and other leaders to improve understanding.  \n    - This aims to reduce disconnect and build consensus around brand direction.  \n    - Feedback cycles will focus on balancing content, design, and audience needs.  \n    - The iterative process supports a stronger final product.\n\n- **Marketing campaigns for Ponce Bank Direct are planned for spring, but the current lack of an ads account is a barrier** (41:30)  \n    - Colin is actively pursuing Google support for account recovery, emailing every three days.  \n    - Christina will begin preparing internal teams for email campaigns and social channel reconnections.  \n    - The sunset of Constant Contact is planned in favor of HubSpot-driven communications.  \n    - These steps support a coordinated go-to-market strategy aligned with the website launch.\n\n- **The team agreed to cancel the regular follow-up meeting as key topics were covered, signaling readiness to focus on next deliverables** (42:25)  \n    - This reflects confidence in current progress and clarity on immediate priorities.  \n    - The team will synchronize internally and provide updates as needed.  \n    - This decision streamlines communication and frees resources for implementation.  \n    - It underscores efficient project management practices.","outline":null,"keywords":["Ponce Bank","Website Design","HubSpot Integration","Brochure Feedback","Buyer’s Intent","Local Market Imagery"],"overview":"- **Website Redesign Focus:** Prioritize modern simplicity and brand cohesion, balancing line drawings and stock images for clarity.\n\n- **Audience Segmentation:** Tailor homepage content for four main segments: consumer, community, investor relations, and recruiting to improve messaging.\n\n- **Visual Updates Needed:** Use current visuals, enhance local relevance, and diversify representation to better resonate with audiences.\n\n- **Content Organization Improvement:** Create distinct navigation for personal and business banking to clarify services and enhance user experience.\n\n- **HubSpot Integration:** Centralize data management for branch locations, ensuring accurate and consistent customer information across platforms.\n\n- **Next Steps Agreed:** Revamp homepage mockup for executive feedback, refine microsites, and prepare marketing campaigns for a coordinated rollout.","action_items":"\n**Christina Zanca**\nProvide additional brochure and sales sheet feedback post-team review this week (06:56)\nCoordinate internal alignment to gain executive buy-in on homepage design iterations (40:20)\nIdentify teams to involve for upcoming email campaigns and social channel reconnections (41:45)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nConfirm receipt and loading of contact records in HubSpot (07:05)\nDeliver a revamped Ponce Bank homepage mockup including main nav, hero placeholders, and footer for investor relations and foundation review (31:39)\nSync and incorporate feedback into all designed pages, including preparing updated brochure and website assets for Friday or later date (40:26)\nContinue communications and follow-up with Google user support for ads account activation (41:13)\nSend updates on test contact loading and HubSpot integration status (41:13)\n\n**Victor Garcia**\nIntroduce buyer’s intent feature discussion for potential Q2 phase launch, explaining data tracking benefits to sales team (37:36)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"0a4ee5a5-7a10-4851-ac35-322c73b34eff","mas